data.description: Presenting an exceptional and intricately crafted home in Fort Lauderdale Beach, this listing displays a creative flair in its interior design. The property comes fully furnished, featuring a stunning spiral staircase leading to more than three terraces and balconies, offering panoramic views of the surroundings. The residence is equipped with wolf appliances, providing a perfect blend of style and functionality. Additionally, the outdoor space boasts a refreshing pool, hot tub with 10 year warranty creating a perfect oasis for relaxation. Ensuring privacy and security, the property is gated. Situated just steps away from the beach, this home offers a luxurious lifestyle. Airbnb money making machine for investors!
